<item>
            <title>[LU-4200] Test failure on test suite conf-sanity test_66: replace nids failed </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4200</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Nathaniel Clark &amp;lt;nathaniel.l.clark@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/d95b0f48-264f-11e3-8f1c-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/d95b0f48-264f-11e3-8f1c-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/2d26cba2-266f-11e3-b741-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/2d26cba2-266f-11e3-b741-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_66 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;replace nids failed&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: conf-sanity 66&lt;/p&gt;</description>
